column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/b31482844b682e888a5c81739b488a182128ce12 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu

I did a full windows+linux+deps build with this, and it worked.
